channel.title: Mysql: Anyone good at it?
channel.description:
Hey, and this is one of my only times asking for help.
Anyone good at mySQL? And, if your here just to say "omFG, I'm not", don't bother posting please.
If you are any good at mySQL, I might have a job for you. (It could pay in the long run)
I don't need someone who is the best at mySQL, just someone who can do things such as highscores, databases etc. Although, if you are really, really good at it, then I guess you can post ;)
